<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">No, they run away from him! The bear pursues them and they hide under the bedsheets. Then there&apos;s a great picture with no words, of the bear going hom<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">No, they run away from him! The bear pursues them and they hide under the bedsheets. Then there's a great picture with no words, of the bear going home looking sad.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
