        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2426739565" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11273645271311972258">In this repetitive story, the reader is taken along on a family’s hunt for a bear. Walking through the grass, traversing a river, and pushing through a snowstorm are only a few of the obstacles they must overcome (each with their own sounds) in order to make it to the bear’s cave. Once they reach the cave and come eye to eye with this bear.... they quickly change their minds and rush back through all the obstacles to the safety of being under the covers. Quite the tale and Neo enjoyed all the od</span>
  <span id="freeText11273645271311972258" style="display:none">In this repetitive story, the reader is taken along on a family’s hunt for a bear. Walking through the grass, traversing a river, and pushing through a snowstorm are only a few of the obstacles they must overcome (each with their own sounds) in order to make it to the bear’s cave. Once they reach the cave and come eye to eye with this bear.... they quickly change their minds and rush back through all the obstacles to the safety of being under the covers. Quite the tale and Neo enjoyed all the odd sounds as the family made their way through the book. He did find it funny that they were determined to find a bear but ran off when they completed their task.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11273645271311972258" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
