        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer431622513" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6395952527443412436">This is a perfect mix of rhyme and repetition, with a good measure of suspense thrown in. <br/>Even better is the ease with which this can be read and performed; you can walk around and have fun with it, and this is exactly what we need in my household. I used this book as part of my storytime assessment at TAFE. Throw on a hat and a pair of binoculars and we were off! It&apos;s a great book to engage with youngsters and hopefully start off with a life long learning of books. Reading is meant to be fun an</span>
  <span id="freeText6395952527443412436" style="display:none">This is a perfect mix of rhyme and repetition, with a good measure of suspense thrown in. <br />Even better is the ease with which this can be read and performed; you can walk around and have fun with it, and this is exactly what we need in my household. I used this book as part of my storytime assessment at TAFE. Throw on a hat and a pair of binoculars and we were off! It's a great book to engage with youngsters and hopefully start off with a life long learning of books. Reading is meant to be fun and this is a perfect example! Go for it if you've got some youngsters nearby.</span>
